# NetcfgWidget
An Android widget that displays IP addresses of all active network interfaces.  This widget acts
an interface to Android's *netcfg* command.

Unlike other widgets commonly found in the PlayStore, this widget only needs Internet permission to work.

## Usage
* Drag the widget to the desktop
* Tap the widget to refresh its contents.

